description: Demolition of existing structures and the phased redevelopment to provide 394 residential dwellings, car parking, bicycle parking, substation, public open space and pedestrian/cycle infrastructure, and other works and improvements (including de- culverting of Pooles Sewer, relocation of gas main, minor alterations to access from New Road and closure of existing secondary accesses, formation of emergency access onto Lamson Road and other associated works) at Dovers Corner Industrial Park, Rainham Trading Estate and Boomes Industrial Estate, New Road, Rainham
